gomodel:SYNGO_1830  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.8 IL-1RAcPb and IL-1RAcP (not shown) requires PTPδ for presynaptic differentiation. Experimental description: - Overexpressed 1RAcP is of mouse species: \"The entire coding sequences of mouse IL-1RAcP, IL-1RAcPb, ...\"\n\"Cell cultures, transfection, and coculture assay. Primary cortical cultures were prepared from mice at postnatal day 0 (P0) essentially as described previously\"" ;
